        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Saint Paul</placeName>
                <date>October 20 5623</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">As I have to acknowledge<lb/> that you always did for me whatever
                you could, and I<lb/> will never for get you, I therefore take myself the<lb/>
                liberty, to beg of you, to give place to my writing to the<lb/> so called
                    <persName>Doctor Wise</persName>, who wish to injure me, and who<lb/> is an
                enemy to any one whoever is not of his opinion;<lb/> I am accused in his paper for
                having left a wife with<lb/> four children, of which I did not wish to give him<lb/>
                any answer. But to you indeed the truth of it is<lb/> when I left <placeName>New
                    York</placeName> I was reengaged in <placeName>Nashville</placeName><lb/>
                directly after the engagement it was blockaded,<lb/> at the same time I sent some
                money if I had any opportunity<lb/> after I came to <placeName>Memphis</placeName>,
                directly, when the blockade<lb/> was open I wrote to my wife. But before I had
                an<lb/> answer from her I became sick and so I was obliged<lb/> to <sic>live</sic>
                <placeName>Memphis</placeName>, and did not wish that another shall write<lb/> to my
                wife and after coming to <placeName>Davenport</placeName> I was in bed about<lb/>
                five weeks, and that kept me beak<add>?</add> from writing till being<lb/> a little
                better, and when I came here on <add>עיה"כ</add> you may ask<lb/>
                <persName>Mr Lion</persName> who was <add>שוחט</add> in
                    <placeName>Cleveland</placeName>, and still it is only<lb/> he who keeps all the
                Israelites here to tune <add>?</add> though being<lb/> himself a business man, if I
                did not, after speaking with<lb/> him one quarter of an hour, write to my family,
                where<lb/> I am and I hope to send for them as soon as possible<lb/> any how, I will
                send them so much money as will be</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>in my power, hoping that you will believe me<lb/> an <sic>especialy</sic> you may be
                convinced of the<lb/> truth thereof from <placeName>Memphis</placeName> from
                        <placeName><sic>davenport</sic></placeName> and<lb/> from here I hope you
                will do so.</p>
            <p>Please God next week I will send you money<lb/> for a dozen of your Religious
                books.</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">I remain</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">your most obedient</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">E. Marcuson</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
